---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Web Presence">
  <section class="section">
    <h1>Web Presence</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Simple, fast websites for small businesses and independent professionals - built to be used on a phone.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section text">
    <h2>What I build</h2>
    <p>
      I build small websites that make you look legitimate and make it easy for people to contact you.
      No complex systems, no endless revisions - just a clean site that does the job.
    </p>

    <ul class="bullets">
      <li>One-page business websites</li>
      <li>Portfolio sites for artists and freelancers</li>
      <li>Small company pages (2-5 pages)</li>
      <li>WhatsApp, phone, email, maps - clear and direct calls to action</li>
      <li>Fast load times and mobile-first layout</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section text">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <ul class="bullets">
      <li>Short intake - what you do, what you offer, how people contact you</li>
      <li>I build the first version</li>
      <li>One revision round to polish text and details</li>
      <li>Launch and shareable link</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="muted">
      If you already have photos and text, it goes faster. If you donâ€™t, I can help you organize it.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section text">
    <h2>Good fit for</h2>
    <ul class="bullets">
      <li>Drivers and transport services</li>
      <li>Local service businesses</li>
      <li>Studios, teachers, coaches</li>
      <li>Artists, DJs, freelancers</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Book a build</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        Send the scope, your location, and the main contact method (WhatsApp / phone / email).
      </p>
      <p class="links">
        <a href="/contact">Go to Contact</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
